  {
    "uid": "doi:10.2139/ssrn.6924659",
    "drop": false,
    "field": "management",
    "role": "agent",
    "bullets": [
      "Preregistered online experiment with 700 participants doing an ideation task to improve Airbnb's business-model alignment with the UN Sustainable Development Goals under three human-AI ensemble configurations.",
      "GPT-4o was embedded in the interface to generate and evaluate ideas as a collaborator; human and AI evaluators both rated outputs, with no accuracy check against ground truth.",
      "Parallel ensembles produced the highest-rated ideas, human-first gave the most novelty and satisfaction, and evaluators preferred ideas generated by their own type."
    ],
